{"tid":2100609,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"川普斥鉅資播放競選廣告 強調77歲拜登太老不適合當總統","createTime":"2020-07-09T07:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T10:23:06.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"546fcbe0cda337a1e649acdf45baeeafdbc4edab","tid":2100609,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕綜合美媒報導，現年74歲美國總統川普已投資數百萬美元在各大媒體上放送競選廣告，批評77歲的拜登年紀太大，不適合當總統，強調拜登缺乏「領導這個國家的力量、耐力和精神毅力」。<br />\n<br />\n據媒體分析數據顯示，自6月中旬以來，這則30秒廣告已經在美國12個州播放，耗資650萬美元（約1.9億台幣），《美聯社》表示，這是今年美國最貴的一則廣告。<br />\n<br />\n美國老齡化協會（American Society of Ageing）主席布蘭卡托（Robert Blancato）批川普團隊，他認為這種抨擊不屬於政治，而是年齡歧視，他指出：「世界不是每個人都會成為種族主義或性別歧視的受害者，但每個人都可能成為年齡歧視的受害者」，而拜登現在正是年齡歧視的受害者。<br />\n<br />\n若拜登在今年的大選中擊敗川普，在11月20日滿78歲的他將會成為美國歷史上年紀最大的總統，原紀錄保持人正是川普，他在2017年上任時為70歲又7個月6天。<br />\n<br />\n有一項調查美國總統年齡和健康狀況的研究指出，拜登有21%的機率無法完成4年的任期，而川普則有15%的可能性無法完成任期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3223023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3223023&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmr%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=08c54ce2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3223023&h=dc11975a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3223023</a>"},{"pid":"78f417abb890a8c81c12fe0a52d2cbebb16169bf","tid":2100609,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"牙豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3174df7ffa07d3bc401b034ab6963384102c0bf6","tid":2100609,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:27:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MVCAm6jSI5I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMVCAm6jSI5I&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmr%2BiaDmtBxIfZa%2Bp1tlHcc8%3D&h=8c40a723\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MVCAm6jSI5I</a>"},{"pid":"9848e3330685e75dd8a2301b63651b9ac90b0d6f","tid":2100609,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"民主黨副總統熱門：Elizabeth Warren<br />\n<br />\n都係老女人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55afb96833ff38498808008bd7a822181ea10c66","tid":2100609,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9848e3330685e75dd8a2301b63651b9ac90b0d6f","tid":2100609,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"民主黨副總統熱門：Elizabeth Warren<br />\n<br />\n都係老女人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:30:46.000Z","msg":"Harris 都ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7070e42999a7a78df087f8e573ea600713aa42d","tid":2100609,"uid":277992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"一個老人比人話年齡歧視另一個老人"},{"pid":"2b1da8c6e0006026a8a574bd485ca78de4d003e8","tid":2100609,"uid":328494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"Anyone but 敗登"},{"pid":"e76747e20a70782f47d465730767fb79fb9ccb96","tid":2100609,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:54:44.000Z","msg":"只係兩個年紀差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da4ccab247af9922be3b9dd853a5330f9b2260a","tid":2100609,"uid":11578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"喂喂喂喂喂"},{"pid":"80159025f4dc7c341e012d2c03049e97fc81aa90","tid":2100609,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:23:06.000Z","msg":"咁77歲真係幾老，美國無人啦咩"}]}